Apple-1 Emulator
================

Portable Apple-1 emulator in C.

Quick start (POSIX):

    ./configure && make
    ./apple1 -r wozmon.bin

Documentation
-------------

Start at documentation/README, then pick your host:

    documentation/README        Index
    documentation/platforms.md    All ports (POSIX, DOS, Windows, Plan 9,
                                  Nspire, VxWorks, FreeRTOS, UnixWare, …)
    documentation/building.md   Autotools, tests, cross-compiles
    documentation/usage.md        CLI options and .conf files
    documentation/configuration.md  Compile-time flags
    documentation/plan9-terminal.md
    documentation/VXWORKS_RTP.md
    documentation/FREERTOS_DEMO.md
    documentation/hardware.md
    documentation/debugger.md

    documentation/manual.md       Deprecated — do not use
